divs: Sighting DetailsMy Wife and I were walking on the mountains, We were overlooking thesea .We decided to take picturs of the local Island.It was a calm DayThe only thing unusal we notices was a commotion on the sea,and a whalewas leaving the area asap, We took some photos of the sea.We took 15 photos and there are ufos on 13 of themOn one photo of the sea there are 8 ufo there ,some are justover the sea,Some are comming out of the sea.I send a photograph to Mr peter Davenport.about 3 weeks ago,he didnt get backto me yet. This photo is of the ufo I call Babyblue because of its blue colorsThis ufo is flying in a formation with 5 or 6 others2B2B2B2B2BOTheres another group far behine them..On another photo theres a group of white ones flying above the sea.There are many different ufo on the photos,Some seems to be almost shapelesslike camouflage.We took the photos of the sea and we didnt see the ufoabut we were only about 1000 yards from themYou can see them much better with an electric light.They are hard to seein the Day light,unless you know where they are in the photographs
